{
  "texts": [
    "Nonetheless, as discussed in Sect. 2.2, applying ML models in IoT environments faces the challenges of enhancing robustness and reducing the resources required by deployment.",
    "LLMs' remote access empowers them to be superior candidates.",
    "LLMs can not only be queried to decipher the raw information but also automatically generate concrete code for carrying out the processing steps.",
    "Execution of these code provides additional insightful information and visualizations, tailored to the user's specific needs.",
    "This capability marks a significant leap in making IoT data more accessible and actionable."
  ]
}